#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an7.25"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.25:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.25:0.2"
msgid "3. Vajjisattakavagga "
msgstr "3. The Vajji Seven "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.25:0.3"
msgid "25. Tatiyasattakasutta "
msgstr "25. Non-Decline for Mendicants (3rd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.23, sc1
msgctxt "an7.25:1.1"
msgid "“Satta vo, bhikkhave, aparihāniye dhamme desessāmi. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you seven principles that prevent decline. "

msgctxt "an7.25:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha … pe … "
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention … "

msgctxt "an7.25:1.3"
msgid "katame ca, bhikkhave, satta aparihāniyā dhammā? "
msgstr "And what are the seven principles that prevent decline? "

msgctxt "an7.25:1.4"
msgid "Yāvakīvañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhū saddhā bhavissanti; vuddhiyeva, bhikkhave, bhikkhūnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihāni. "
msgstr "As long as the mendicants are faithful … "

#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an7.25:2.1"
msgid "Yāvakīvañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhū hirimanto bhavissanti … pe … "
msgstr "conscientious … "

#. VAR: ottappino → ottāpino (bj)
msgctxt "an7.25:2.2"
msgid "ottappino bhavissanti … "
msgstr "prudent … "

msgctxt "an7.25:2.3"
msgid "bahussutā bhavissanti … "
msgstr "learned … "

msgctxt "an7.25:2.4"
msgid "āraddhavīriyā bhavissanti … "
msgstr "energetic … "

msgctxt "an7.25:2.5"
msgid "satimanto bhavissanti … "
msgstr "mindful … "

msgctxt "an7.25:2.6"
msgid "paññavanto bhavissanti; vuddhiyeva, bhikkhave, bhikkhūnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihāni. "
msgstr "wise, they can expect growth, not decline. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an7.25:3.1"
msgid "Yāvakīvañca, bhikkhave, ime satta aparihāniyā dhammā bhikkhūsu ṭhassanti, imesu ca sattasu aparihāniyesu dhammesu bhikkhū sandississanti; vuddhiyeva, bhikkhave, bhikkhūnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihānī”ti. "
msgstr "As long as these seven principles that prevent decline last among the mendicants, and as long as the mendicants are seen following them, they can expect growth, not decline.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.25:3.2"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

